1 WHEREAS, Melissa Hortman served as speaker of the Minnesota House of
2 Representatives from 2019 until January 2025; and
3 WHEREAS, Speaker Emerita Hortman was married to the late Mark Hortman, and
4 she was the mother of two children: Colin and Sophie; and
5 WHEREAS, Melissa Hortman was a consummate public servant and beloved
6 member of her community; she will be deeply missed, but the legacy of her service to and
7 compassion for the citizens of Minnesota shall live on in perpetuity.
8 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
9 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby express heartfelt condolences on the death of
10 Minnesota House Speaker Emerita Melissa Hortman; does hereby extend enduring
11 appreciation for her dedicated service to the state of Minnesota; and does hereby extend
12 sincere wishes that her family, friends, former colleagues, and loved ones find comfort in
13 their shared memories of her beautiful life.
